Title: adapt calculation of memory usage to match docker 20.10
Class: fix
Compatible: compat
Component: checks
Date: 1615795909
Edition: cre
Knowledge: doc
Level: 1
Version: 2.1.0b1

Docker 20.10 changed the way how memory usage of docker containers is
calculated, the docker check was adapted accordingly.

See https://github.com/docker/cli/pull/2415 for more information.
